  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tiger Simulator</strong> is a casual <strong>high-score</strong> game. You're a tiger that has been set loose in a <strong>big city</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run and jump</strong> around a sprawling city and <strong>attack</strong> all sorts of people to <strong>get points</strong>; attack one right after the other to get bonus points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How many humans can you <strong>send flying</strong> before time runs out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of each run, receive your score number and <strong>try again</strong> for an even higher score!</p>",
